ass=\"cl-293c8f84\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">NewComp</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-293cb539\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f8e\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">164,482,009</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-293cb538\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f84\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">IncreaseDuetoRaise</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-293cb539\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f8e\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">9,310,302</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-293cb538\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f84\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">Burden_25</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-293cb539\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f8e\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">2,327,576</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-293cb538\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f84\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">Burden_40</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-293cb539\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f8e\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">3,724,121</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-293cb538\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f84\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">TotalCost_25</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-293cb539\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f8e\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">11,637,878</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-293cb540\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f84\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">TotalCost_40</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-293cb541\"><p class=\"cl-293c8f8e\"><span class=\"cl-2935b452\">13,034,423</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\nTherefore to raise everyone's pay by 6% the total cost would be between $11.6M - $13M \n\n* The cost for 6% raises is $9.3M\n* The additional employeer cost due to payroll taxes / benfits: between $2.3M and $3.7M",
